---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const title = '關於兩隻熊 ｜ 未來的觀測者';
const description = '誰說旅遊只能留在當下？兩隻熊異象觀測站，帶你旅行到未來的邊境。';
---

<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <BaseHead title={title} description={description} />
  <style is:global>
    .about-page {
      background: #020a14;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .about-hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }
    .about-grid-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,245,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,245,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .about-grid-bg::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%, transparent 40%, #020a14 100%);
    }
    .about-hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 820px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .about-eyebrow {
      font-size: .75rem;
      letter-spacing: .25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #00f5ff;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: .75rem;
    }
    .about-eyebrow::before,
    .about-eyebrow::after {
      content: '';
      display: inline-block;
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: #00f5ff;
      opacity: .5;
    }
    .about-hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin: 0 0 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #00f5ff 50%, #a78bfa 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .about-manifesto {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.2rem);
      line-height: 2;
      color: #94a3b8;
      border-left: 3px solid #00f5ff;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      text-align: left;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    }
    .about-manifesto strong {
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* ── SECTION WRAPPER ── */
    .about-section {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .about-section-label {
      font-size: .7rem;
      letter-spacing: .3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #00f5ff;
      margin-bottom: .75rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .about-section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0 0 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .about-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,245,255,.12);
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── WHY CARDS ── */
    .why-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .why-card {
      background: rgba(0,245,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,245,255,.15);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: border-color .3s, transform .3s;
    }
    .why-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(0,245,255,.5);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .why-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .why-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      margin: 0 0 .75rem;
    }
    .why-card p {
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── RULES ── */
    .rules-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
    .rule-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 3rem 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .rule-emoji {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: .1rem;
    }
    .rule-item h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      margin: 0 0 .4rem;
    }
    .rule-item p {
      font-size: .88rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── BEAR CREW ── */
    .crew-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .crew-card {
      position: relative;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,245,255,.05) 0%, rgba(167,139,250,.05) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.25);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .crew-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00f5ff, #a78bfa);
    }
    .crew-bear-icon {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }
    .crew-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin: 0 0 .5rem;
    }
    .crew-role {
      font-size: .75rem;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #00f5ff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .crew-card p {
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .crew-tags {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .5rem;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
    }
    .crew-tag {
      font-size: .7rem;
      padding: .2rem .65rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(167,139,250,.15);
      color: #a78bfa;
      border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,.3);
    }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .about-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 5rem 1.5rem 6rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-cta::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 600px; max-width: 90%;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #00f5ff, transparent);
    }
    .about-cta p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .about-cta-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f5ff, #a78bfa);
      color: #020a14;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .about-cta-btn:hover {
      opacity: .9;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .about-support-note {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: #334155;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }
    .about-support-note a {
      color: #475569;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding-bottom: 1px;
      transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .about-support-note a:hover {
      color: #94a3b8;
      border-bottom-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .about-manifesto { font-size: 1rem; }
      .rule-item { grid-template-columns: 2.5rem 1fr; }
      .about-eyebrow  { font-size: .85rem; }
      .rule-text      { font-size: .95rem; }
      .rule-label     { font-size: .85rem; }
      .stat-label     { font-size: .85rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="about-page">
  <Header />

  <!-- ── LAYER 1: MANIFESTO ── -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-grid-bg"></div>
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <div class="about-eyebrow">異象觀測站 · 數位避難所</div>
      <h1>關於兩隻熊<br/>未來的觀測者</h1>
      <blockquote class="about-manifesto">
        誰說旅遊只能留在當下？<br/>
        過去，我們用雙腳記錄世界的風景；<br/>
        現在，我們用<strong>數據、玄學與危機意識</strong>，<br/>
        帶你「旅行」到未來的邊境。<br/><br/>
        歡迎來到數位避難所，<br/>
        這裡是<strong>兩隻熊的異象觀測站</strong>。
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="about-divider" />

  <!-- ── LAYER 2: WHY ── -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-label">為什麼建立這個網站</div>
    <div class="about-section-title">我們能為你解決什麼</div>
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>抗衡焦慮的儀表板</h3>
        <p>世界變化太快，傳統新聞只會散播恐慌。我們整合即時行情、地緣風險與天災數據，把焦慮變成可視化的客觀指數。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">🔮</div>
        <h3>探索未知的先知百科</h3>
        <p>從 Baba Vanga 到比格斯，我們不盲信預言，但我們記錄天時的軌跡，在九運的混亂中尋找可能出現的轉折點。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card">
        <div class="why-icon">🕯️</div>
        <h3>亂世之中的心靈錨點</h3>
        <p>無論世界怎麼變，這裡提供純粹的個人命理指引與匿名許願池，讓每個迷茫的靈魂在數位荒漠中找到一盞明燈。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="about-divider" />

  <!-- ── LAYER 3: RULES ── -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-label">觀測站核心守則</div>
    <div class="about-section-title">我們的態度與承諾</div>
    <div class="rules-list">
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="rule-emoji">📊</div>
        <div>
          <h3>數據絕對客觀</h3>
          <p>我們的金融走馬燈與全球異常事件（如地震、國際局勢）皆串接第三方權威 API，只呈現事實，不加工恐慌。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="rule-emoji">🔮</div>
        <div>
          <h3>觀點保持開放</h3>
          <p>預言與命理系統是古老智慧與未來模型的結合，我們將其數據化、趣味化，提供大眾不同的思考維度，而非宣揚絕對真理。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rule-item">
        <div class="rule-emoji">🕯️</div>
        <div>
          <h3>社群互相守望</h3>
          <p>這是一個專為「對未來保持警覺、拒絕盲從」的人打造的地下公會，我們共同應對金融重組與時代變革，不孤單前行。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="about-divider" />

  <!-- ── LAYER 4: BEAR CREW ── -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-label">創作者檔案</div>
    <div class="about-section-title">認識兩隻熊</div>
    <div class="crew-grid">
      <div class="crew-card">
        <span class="crew-bear-icon">🐻</span>
        <h3>泰迪</h3>
        <div class="crew-role">技術架構 · 數據觀測</div>
        <p>負責在後端編織 Gemini AI 的靈魂、串接全球地震與 TradingView 數據，負責建造這個數位避難所的防空洞。每一行程式碼，都是為了讓你在亂世中看得更清楚。</p>
        <div class="crew-tags">
          <span class="crew-tag">AI 工程</span>
          <span class="crew-tag">數據串接</span>
          <span class="crew-tag">全端開發</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="crew-card">
        <span class="crew-bear-icon">🐼</span>
        <h3>熊蓋讚</h3>
        <div class="crew-role">命理研究 · 趨勢解碼</div>
        <p>負責解碼六十四卦、梳理國際預言家脈絡，在亂世中為迷航者點燈。把晦澀難懂的預言語言翻譯成每個人都能理解的生存地圖。</p>
        <div class="crew-tags">
          <span class="crew-tag">易經命理</span>
          <span class="crew-tag">預言研究</span>
          <span class="crew-tag">趨勢分析</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CTA ── -->
  <div class="about-cta">
    <p>準備好進入未來了嗎？</p>
    <a href="/" class="about-cta-btn">
      前往首頁控制台 →
    </a>
    <p class="about-support-note">
      這個網站是兩隻熊在正職之外花時間維護的。<br>
      如果這裡讓你有收穫，歡迎<a href="https://ko-fi.com/twobear2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">請我們喝杯咖啡 ☕</a>，讓我們繼續走下去。
    </p>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
